  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a blender, combine almond butter, yuzu juice, soy sauce, and honey.",
    "Blend until smooth.",
    "Add saudi spices and blend until combined.",
    "Place chicken breast in a shallow dish and brush with sesame oil.",
    "Pour almond sauce over chicken breast and marinate for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Remove chicken from marinade and grill for 5-7 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "Slice chicken into bite-sized pieces.",
    "Serve with grilled almonds and green onions.",
